         Mysk,</P><P>Sol Ro temple has quests for 4 focus items, broom, torch, stein, showvel. These work on ALL elemental pets up to lvl 50, boosting stats and hit points.</P><P>Staffs of Elemental Mastery work on all elemental pets (bar epic) from lvl 49+. They add +1 level to pet, and affect them more powerfuly in other areas than the Sol Ro items, for example, water 60 pet has actually got crap hit points as it's a rogue, but summoned with focus staff it has same hit points as earth pet (lots) and is a MUCH nastier pet over all.<BR>The astaffs have NO stats by way, 2hand blunt, and have Reclaim energy as clickable effect.<BR>Water staff drops from Phinigel Autropos in Kedge, rare drop.<BR>Air staff quest is, ugh, horrific, think I've only met ONE mage with air staff and thats cause she got it ages ago. Items used in Air staff quest are: Sweet Nectar, a Crown of Elemental Mastery, a Large Diamond and a Djinni's Stave. Those who've done Sky know why thats a **** joke /sigh.<BR>Earth staff drops from Magi Ptasi in Hate (miniboss so you'll understand pain in that)<BR>Fire staff from Mistress of Scorn (again miniboss in Hate)</P><P>Hope that helps :)</P><P>Redorious<BR>Archmage<BR>Karana</P><P><BR><a href="http://www.silverblades-suitcase.com/" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.silverblades-suitcase.com/artofadreamer/3d/excalibur2thumb.jpg" border=0></a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
